<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, August 2 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index
closed at 624.09 points Monday, up 1.40 percent from Sunday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
A daily bulletin of the bourse said 367,081 shares changed
hands in 311 deals, and the turnover was 6,998,081 dinars (6.36
million U.S. dollars). 
</P>
</TEXT>
