<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, August 2 (Xinhua) -- U.S. President Bill Clinton
Monday announced emergency drought assistance for farmers and
money for providing air conditioners and fans for the elderly and
poor to deal with the current heat wave.
</P>
