parties announced identical programs to gear up their
anti-government movement, including a week-long program of rallies
between August 7 and 13, demonstrations before district
commissioners' offices across the country on August 18, a big
procession in Dhaka on August 30 and a siege of the Bangladesh
Secretariat on September 12.
