<HEADLINE> Nepal, Mauritius Sign Agreements on Investment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, August 3 (Xinhua) -- Nepal and Mauritius signed two
agreements on investment promotion and protection as well as
double taxation avoidance here Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Nepali Finance Minister Mahesh Acharya and Minister of Finance
Dr. Vasant J. Bunwaree of Mauritius signed the documents on behalf
of their respective governments.
</P>
<P>
