dollars) transfer from Spanish giant Real Madrid to Arsenal on
Monday in a deal which reportedly halved his weekly salary from 40,
000 pounds (64,400 U.S. dollars) per week to 20,000 pounds (32,200
U.S. dollars) per week.
</P>
<P>
Suker, who joined Real Madrid in 1996, had a falling out with
coach John Toshack last season, which prompted his move. 
